list.abstract: Painter是专业的自然媒介（natural media）电脑绘画软件，原由Fractal Design开发，后经MetaCreations转给了Corel，支持windows系统平台。 Painter具有绘画、素描、二维创作的功能，拥有丰富的笔刷工具，可以绘制出各种风格的画作作品。

yingyinNormal.en: The painter, the calligrapher, they can be said to have Kung Fu.
yingyinNormal.zh: 画家，书法家，都可以说是功夫了得之人。

yingyinNormal.en: You are also a very accomplished painter, aren't you? Well, how can I not be?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你同时是个高明的画家是吗？是啊，我怎么会不是呢？

yingyinNormal.en: A house painter. He used to be a house painter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 粉刷工人，他以前是粉刷工人。

yingyinNormal.en: Now it's George's turn. What a great painter you are, George. There, the painting is finished. Hooray.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在该你了乔治。你画得真是太好了，乔治！好了，我们的画完成了。好嘞！

yingyinNormal.en: One of Sydney's famous sons, Paul Hogan, the star Crocodile Dundee, was a painter on the bridge before he hit the big time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 《鳄鱼先生》演员保罗霍根贵为悉尼其中一个出名的儿子，不过在他成名之前，曾经是这条大桥的油漆工人。
